data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home with a spacious open floor plan. Highlights include a modern kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, a versatile office or flex space on the main level, hardwood floors throughout, and a total electric setup for efficiency. Upstairs, you'll find a roomy master suite with a dual-sink master bath and walk-in closet, along with a laundry room, large loft area for added living space. The backyard offers a private oasis with a patio for entertaining. This home combines elegance, functionality, and modern amenities—perfect for creating lasting memories. THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR NO DOWN PAYMENT-ASK ME FOR DETAILS & LENDER INFO. Don't miss out!
